Sarkozy Says France, Germany Share Support for ECB Independence

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-10-23T15:08:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/sarkozy-says-france-germany-share-support-for-ecb-independence.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
said France shares  Germany ’s support for the independence of the
 European Central Bank , responding to reports of divisions
between the two countries. “No solution is viable if not
supported by all European institutions,” Sarkozy told reporters
today at a joint briefing in Brussels with Germany’s  Angela Merkel . “It’s a team work.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
 hfouquet1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  